01:00:33.724 --> 01:00:34.304
rejected.

01:00:35.385 --> 01:00:39.108
Ignore God's teaching and God will ignore

01:00:39.148 --> 01:00:40.871
you.

01:00:40.911 --> 01:00:44.873
It's all simple, direct, irrefutable,

01:00:46.175 --> 01:00:47.376
and inalterable.

01:00:50.119 --> 01:00:50.259
Now,

01:00:50.278 --> 01:00:51.800
for those who are thinking this through,

01:00:52.764 --> 01:00:56.230
Yahowah's dissertation in Mizmowr,

01:00:56.311 --> 01:00:58.974
in the midst of his appraisal of his

01:00:59.014 --> 01:01:00.577
son, our Messiah, Dowd,

01:01:00.597 --> 01:01:03.181
affirms that from God's perspective,

01:01:04.001 --> 01:01:06.927
the king walked out of the pages of

01:01:06.967 --> 01:01:07.527
the Towrah.

01:01:09.365 --> 01:01:12.367
doing so when he fulfilled Pesach, Matsah,

01:01:12.427 --> 01:01:14.547
and Bikuwrym, which is why they mattered,

01:01:14.726 --> 01:01:15.927
which is why they work,

01:01:16.487 --> 01:01:18.327
which is why we can benefit from them.

01:01:19.248 --> 01:01:21.429
And he's going to do the same thing

01:01:21.509 --> 01:01:25.769
again when he fulfills Kipurym and then

01:01:25.849 --> 01:01:28.831
again Sukah.

01:01:28.851 --> 01:01:33.132
Dowd is the living embodiment of the

01:01:33.172 --> 01:01:35.431
Towrah.

01:01:35.492 --> 01:01:38.112
He is the Word of God made flesh.

01:01:40.373 --> 01:01:43.295
Now understand, Dowd,

01:01:44.657 --> 01:01:47.440
you focus on him and come to comprehend

01:01:48.159 --> 01:01:49.702
everything that he represents,

01:01:49.762 --> 01:01:52.664
and then you contemplate what the Towrah

01:01:52.704 --> 01:01:53.065
says.

01:01:53.804 --> 01:01:55.706
Then you're in a position to accept and

01:01:55.746 --> 01:01:56.827
embrace God's Son.

01:01:58.028 --> 01:01:59.771
And by doing so,

01:01:59.831 --> 01:02:02.273
you're also accepting and embracing

01:02:02.753 --> 01:02:04.215
Yahowah's teaching and guidance.

01:02:04.275 --> 01:02:06.297
They go hand in hand.

01:02:08.594 --> 01:02:09.474
Now, by contrast,

01:02:09.514 --> 01:02:13.576
the corollary is that replacing Dowd with

01:02:13.635 --> 01:02:17.177
Paul and Jesus, Akiba and Bar Kokhba,

01:02:17.958 --> 01:02:19.878
Muhammad and his pet Allah,

01:02:20.577 --> 01:02:22.659
or Maga and Trump, the Rahab,

01:02:23.458 --> 01:02:25.539
is to be seen rejecting the Towrah and

01:02:25.599 --> 01:02:29.260
choosing to die.

01:02:29.300 --> 01:02:30.481
Religion and politics,

01:02:31.440 --> 01:02:33.101
they both damn souls.

01:02:34.786 --> 01:02:35.728
Now said another way,

01:02:36.188 --> 01:02:38.130
the reason that Dowd's fulfillment of

01:02:38.170 --> 01:02:39.010
Pesach, Matsah,

01:02:39.050 --> 01:02:41.692
and Baquedah matter is because he was

01:02:41.853 --> 01:02:45.394
delivering the promised benefits presented

01:02:45.554 --> 01:02:49.277
in and attested to within Yahowah's Towrah.

01:02:50.318 --> 01:02:51.360
They are inseparable.

01:02:52.440 --> 01:02:54.983
The sacrifice on Pesach apart from the

01:02:55.023 --> 01:02:57.063
Towrah is nothing more than a torturous

01:02:57.123 --> 01:02:59.887
experience resulting in death, not life.

01:03:00.822 --> 01:03:04.865
Matsah becomes meaningless and meritless.

01:03:05.806 --> 01:03:08.949
There is no resolving our guilt without

01:03:08.989 --> 01:03:10.610
what the Towrah promises.

01:03:11.811 --> 01:03:14.514
There is no Bakowrim or firstborn children

01:03:15.153 --> 01:03:17.356
and no purpose to a Bakowr firstborn son.

01:03:19.838 --> 01:03:22.681
And this means that everything Dowd agreed

01:03:22.740 --> 01:03:23.141
to do

01:03:24.405 --> 01:03:28.168
And this life in thirty three C.E.

01:03:28.188 --> 01:03:31.351
year four thousand year was described in

01:03:31.391 --> 01:03:32.012
the Towrah.

01:03:32.911 --> 01:03:35.594
It all occurred on the right day and

01:03:35.634 --> 01:03:37.335
was done in the right way,

01:03:37.835 --> 01:03:40.657
exactly as the Towrah prescribes,

01:03:41.157 --> 01:03:44.161
which makes that counterfeit of Jesus

01:03:44.201 --> 01:03:47.882
Christ so reprehensible because nothing he

01:03:47.922 --> 01:03:50.704
does is consistent with the Towrah.

01:03:51.106 --> 01:03:52.706
Well, everything though did.

01:03:57.516 --> 01:04:01.360
It's the Towrah that makes Pesach, Matsah,

01:04:01.739 --> 01:04:04.942
and Bikuwrym matter.

01:04:04.961 --> 01:04:08.005
Now the dates aren't random either.

01:04:08.025 --> 01:04:09.045
There was no Last Supper.

01:04:10.106 --> 01:04:10.847
No one died.

01:04:11.706 --> 01:04:13.307
There was no napping in the tomb.

01:04:14.108 --> 01:04:16.409
There was no resurrection of a dead body

01:04:16.489 --> 01:04:16.771
either.

01:04:19.032 --> 01:04:19.773
On Passover,

01:04:19.833 --> 01:04:22.394
Dowd's disposable body served as the lamb.

01:04:23.134 --> 01:04:25.215
The remains were destroyed that night.

01:04:26.615 --> 01:04:27.735
During un-yeasted bread,

01:04:27.795 --> 01:04:30.036
Dowd Soul carried our guilt and his own

01:04:30.097 --> 01:04:32.759
into shield, depositing it there,

01:04:32.858 --> 01:04:33.978
never to be seen again,

01:04:34.719 --> 01:04:37.460
rendering the beneficiaries innocent.

01:04:39.061 --> 01:04:40.503
Then on firstborn children,

01:04:41.422 --> 01:04:45.664
Dowd Sol returned right to Shamaym to be

01:04:45.704 --> 01:04:46.646
with his father again.

01:04:48.260 --> 01:04:50.842
making it possible for us to be similarly

01:04:50.902 --> 01:04:52.902
enriched, empowered, enabled,

01:04:54.003 --> 01:04:56.405
entering the seventh dimension as God's

01:04:56.445 --> 01:04:57.266
covenant family.

01:04:59.748 --> 01:05:02.010
There are no baby gods.

01:05:02.030 --> 01:05:03.311
There are no dying gods.

01:05:04.231 --> 01:05:06.092
There are no resurrected gods.

01:05:06.994 --> 01:05:08.114
There are no warlords,

01:05:08.275 --> 01:05:09.795
no religious replacements,

01:05:10.476 --> 01:05:13.739
no New Testaments, no Talmuds, no church.

01:05:14.695 --> 01:05:17.137
No synagogues, no clerics, no rabbis,

01:05:17.217 --> 01:05:18.958
no Jesus, nor Hashem,

01:05:19.838 --> 01:05:22.280
no Christianity or Judaism, no Easter,

01:05:22.340 --> 01:05:28.945
no Purim, no Christians, and no Hanukkah.

01:05:29.025 --> 01:05:36.010
It's Yahowah, Towrah, Covenant, Mowedym, Dowd.

01:05:40.632 --> 01:05:42.414
That is what I would recommend.

01:05:44.121 --> 01:05:46.601
To suggest or protest otherwise,

01:05:47.521 --> 01:05:51.762
quite frankly, is to call God a liar.

01:05:51.822 --> 01:05:55.643
Now, that's not recommended.

01:05:55.684 --> 01:05:55.804
Now,

01:05:55.864 --> 01:05:57.503
one last thought before we close this

01:05:57.563 --> 01:05:58.025
program.

01:05:59.164 --> 01:06:02.405
All four verbs attributable to our choices

01:06:02.465 --> 01:06:04.826
regarding accepting or rejecting Yahowah's

01:06:04.865 --> 01:06:07.847
instructions in that prayer pronouncement

01:06:08.626 --> 01:06:11.288
were scribed in the imperfect conjugation.

01:06:12.693 --> 01:06:12.833
Well,

01:06:12.853 --> 01:06:15.896
the one attributable to God was presented

01:06:15.936 --> 01:06:18.938
in the perfect conjugation.

01:06:19.259 --> 01:06:21.840
Now shaped by the ongoing and habitual

01:06:21.880 --> 01:06:23.262
nature of the imperfect.

01:06:23.722 --> 01:06:26.324
This means that regardless of what we have

01:06:26.364 --> 01:06:27.244
done in the past,

01:06:28.005 --> 01:06:31.429
the moment we come to our senses and

01:06:31.489 --> 01:06:33.710
we stop rebelling against Chawah,

01:06:34.150 --> 01:06:36.813
we are no longer held accountable for our

01:06:36.873 --> 01:06:37.873
prior defiance.

01:06:39.539 --> 01:06:40.260
And with God,

01:06:40.860 --> 01:06:45.384
the time limited expression for the

01:06:45.483 --> 01:06:49.005
perfect conjugation means that his death

01:06:49.045 --> 01:06:52.547
sentence is no longer applicable based

01:06:52.588 --> 01:06:54.389
upon our change in attitude.

01:06:54.829 --> 01:06:56.289
It's the best of both worlds.

01:06:57.530 --> 01:07:02.193
It makes this exceedingly easy for us.

01:07:03.114 --> 01:07:04.534
Just stop being wrong.

01:07:06.195 --> 01:07:07.277
And then you appear right.

01:07:09.672 --> 01:07:09.992
Of course,

01:07:10.032 --> 01:07:12.994
this means that Paul lied when he claimed

01:07:13.034 --> 01:07:15.114
that a single violation of the Towrah was

01:07:15.376 --> 01:07:16.456
eternally damning.

01:07:17.115 --> 01:07:18.157
The opposite is true.

01:07:20.157 --> 01:07:22.059
No matter what we have done,

01:07:22.259 --> 01:07:23.639
once we refrain from it,

01:07:23.978 --> 01:07:25.739
we are no longer subject to the

01:07:25.780 --> 01:07:27.661
consequence.

01:07:27.740 --> 01:07:28.722
That said,

01:07:29.501 --> 01:07:34.443
our change gets us off the hook,

01:07:34.503 --> 01:07:36.304
but it does not grant us access to

01:07:36.344 --> 01:07:36.644
heaven.

01:07:37.766 --> 01:07:38.085
For that,

01:07:39.045 --> 01:07:44.389
We must embrace the lessons of this song.

01:07:44.429 --> 01:07:46.471
So we will return to this point when

01:07:46.550 --> 01:07:51.574
we resume tomorrow here on the Yahowah Vlog.

01:07:52.255 --> 01:07:53.516
I thank you for listening.

01:07:53.615 --> 01:07:55.538
And even if you were one of those

01:07:55.577 --> 01:07:56.257
who was napping,

01:07:56.297 --> 01:08:00.001
maybe you will observe or benefit from it

01:08:00.021 --> 01:08:00.842
from osmosis.

01:08:00.882 --> 01:08:01.601
We will see.

01:08:02.123 --> 01:08:03.643
But thank you so much for being with

01:08:03.704 --> 01:08:03.884
us.

01:08:04.364 --> 01:08:05.025
I am Craig Winn,

01:08:05.445 --> 01:08:07.686
and this has been the Yahowah Vlog.

01:08:09.329 --> 01:08:10.952
Hey there, thanks for tuning in.

01:08:11.153 --> 01:08:12.016
That was Fetch.

01:08:12.157 --> 01:08:13.099
Gotta run now.

01:08:13.320 --> 01:08:15.065
Catch y'all on our next podcast.